---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | DevTools Hub" description="DevTools Hub terms of service. Use of this site is subject to these terms.">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-1 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 dark:text-white">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 mb-12 dark:text-gray-400">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none dark:prose-invert space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">1. Acceptance</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">By using DevTools Hub, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the site.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2. Use of Tools</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">All tools are provided free of charge for lawful purposes. You are responsible for the data you process using our tools. Do not use the tools for illegal activities, malware development, or any purpose that violates applicable laws.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">3. No Warranty</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">The tools and content on DevTools Hub are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We strive for accuracy but make no guarantees about tool output, guide content, or site availability.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">DevTools Hub and its operators are not liable for any damages arising from the use or inability to use the site or its tools.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">5. Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">6. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Questions about these terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:miraclehuang611@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">miraclehuang611@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>